data.description: MOVE in READY home in TAMPA BAY GOLF & COUNTRY CLUB!  Crisp Clean Curb Appeal with Decorative Epoxy driveway, Rock landscape and Screened front entry with Arches and Gutters, Welcomes you to your new home!  Popular floorplan with Dining area, Great Room with 4 foot extension and Kitchen all OPEN for easy entertaining!  Gleaming Granite counters and Center Island/Breakfast Bar with Warm wood cabinets with crown molding, eat in dinette area and formal dining area with Ceramic Tile floors thru common areas!  Sliding doors to enclosed and extended lanai with new wood look tile floors and mounted TV.  Owners retreat is Spacious with the 4 foot extension offering a sitting area and bath ensuite, Large Tile shower with a seat, dual sinks in Granite vanity and separate water closet for commode plus walk in closet.  Guest bedroom and bathroom with tub/shower combo are at the front of the home for privacy.  Double doors off foyer offer a FLEX room with a closet that is set up as the 3rd bedroom... would make a great Den/Office or Fitness area!  Enjoy the Amenities in this 55+ Man-guard gated community: Private streets to drive Golf carts on, Clubhouse with full service Restaurant with stage, dance floor and banquet facilities, Pub/grille overlooking Golf course, Card rooms, game rooms, Activities center with Billiards, Poker tables and state of the art Fitness Center, Community Center with arts and crafts, Bingo, card tables, yoga and exercise classes plus meeting space, 2 swimming pools; 1 resort style heated pool & 1 freeform adult only unheated pool, Tennis, Pickleball, Dog parks, Shuffleboard, Cornhole, onsite entertainment, planned activities and travel excursions!  Located North of Tampa, just off I 75 with easy access to Premium outlets of Wesley Chapel, Wiregrass Mall, The Krate, Dueling pianos, restaurants, movie theater, comedy club and putt-putt at the Grove, Ocala, Orlando, International Airports and the Gulf Beaches!  CALL TODAY!
